GIVEAWAY🎉 -CLOSED-
Want to win a free basque cheesecake with free delivery? Here's how! 
1. Follow us @whiskingbakes
2. Tag 3 friends in the comments below
3. Comment where's the first place you want to travel to after covid19 dies down and why!
4. Share this post on your IG story & tag us
(private accounts can ss your IG story and DM me as proof) 
That's all!!! Contest ends next Friday 5th June 2359. Winner will be announced on 6th June 1900. Delivery will be made on Sunday 7th June!
